SECTION C: ANIMATIONS — FRAMER MOTION PATTERNS
================================================================================

Use Framer Motion for ALL animations. Follow these exact patterns:

C.1  PAGE/CARD ENTRANCE
     ───────────────────
     Every card and section on page load:
       <motion.div
         initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
         animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
         transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}
       >

C.2  STAGGERED CHILDREN (for lists, grids)
     ──────────────────────────────────────
     Parent:
       <motion.div initial="hidden" animate="visible"
         variants={{ visible: { transition: { staggerChildren: 0.05 } } }}>

     Each child:
       <motion.div variants={{
         hidden: { opacity: 0, y: 20 },
         visible: { opacity: 1, y: 0 }
       }}>

C.3  HOVER EFFECTS (for interactive cards)
     ─────────────────────────────────────
       whileHover={{ scale: 1.02, boxShadow: '0 20px 40px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1)' }}

C.4  BUTTON PRESS
     ─────────────
       whileTap={{ scale: 0.97 }}

C.5  TAB TRANSITIONS (AnimatePresence)
     ─────────────────────────────────
       <AnimatePresence mode="wait">
         <motion.div key={activeTab}
           initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 10 }}
           animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
           exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -10 }}
         >

C.6  MODAL ANIMATION
     ────────────────
     Backdrop:
       initial={{ opacity: 0 }} animate={{ opacity: 1 }} exit={{ opacity: 0 }}

     Modal body:
       initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95, y: 20 }}
       animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1, y: 0 }}
       exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95, y: 20 }}

C.7  TOAST NOTIFICATIONS
     ────────────────────
     Slide in from right:
       initial={{ opacity: 0, x: 100 }}
       animate={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }}
       exit={{ opacity: 0, x: 100 }}

C.8  NAVBAR HIDE/SHOW (Tesla-style)
     ──────────────────────────────
     Use useScroll() + useMotionValueEvent() from framer-motion:
       - Track scrollY direction
       - Hide (y: -100) when scrolling DOWN past 80px
       - Show (y: 0) when scrolling UP (5px threshold)
       - Transition: duration 0.35, ease [0.32, 0.72, 0, 1]

     Navbar design: floating pill
       - Fixed top, max-w-5xl, mx-auto, rounded-2xl
       - Transparent at top, darker glass after scroll
       - pt-3 for floating gap from top edge

C.9  ACTIVE TAB INDICATOR
     ─────────────────────
     Use motion.div with layoutId for smooth sliding indicator:
       <motion.div layoutId="activeTab"
         className="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/20 to-green-500/20
                    rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/30"
         transition={{ type: 'spring', bounce: 0.2, duration: 0.6 }}
       />

C.10 LOADING SPINNER
     ────────────────
     Use this pattern for loading states:
       <div className="w-8 h-8 border-2 border-emerald-500 border-t-transparent
                       rounded-full animate-spin" />

C.11 MOBILE SIDEBAR SLIDE
     ─────────────────────
       initial={{ x: -280 }} animate={{ x: 0 }} exit={{ x: -280 }}
     With backdrop: fixed inset-0 bg-black/50


