2.  'use client' — Every component using useState, useEffect, useRouter,
    framer-motion, or browser APIs MUST have 'use client' at the top.

3.  ANIMATIONS EVERYWHERE — Every card entrance, tab switch, modal open/close,
    and page transition MUST use Framer Motion. No static pages.

4.  GLASSMORPHISM CONSISTENCY — Every card, sidebar, topbar, modal, and dropdown
    MUST use the glass effect (bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10).

5.  ROUNDED CORNERS — rounded-2xl for cards, rounded-xl for buttons and inputs,
    rounded-lg for small elements. Never use sharp corners.

6.  EMERALD AS PRIMARY — The primary accent color is ALWAYS emerald green
    (from-emerald-500 to-green-500). Use it for CTAs, active states, gradients.

7.  LUCIDE ICONS ONLY — Use lucide-react for ALL icons. Never use emoji or
    other icon libraries in the UI components.

8.  RESPONSIVE — Every page MUST work on mobile. Use responsive classes:
    grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4, hidden md:flex, etc.

9.  NO INLINE STYLES — Use Tailwind classes only. No style={{}} objects
    unless absolutely necessary for dynamic values.

10. SSR SAFETY — All localStorage/window access MUST check
    typeof window !== 'undefined' first.

11. TOAST FOR FEEDBACK — Every user action (save, delete, submit, pay) MUST
    show a toast notification confirming success or error.

12. LOADING STATES — Every async action (data fetch, form submit) MUST show
    a loading spinner or skeleton while processing.

13. EMPTY STATES — Every list/table MUST have an empty state message when
    no data exists instead of showing nothing.

14. suppressHydrationWarning — Add to <html> tag to prevent browser extension
    hydration errors.


